dmca.title: Claim of Infringement of Rust Control Site
dmca.body:
1) The copyrighted work of mine that is being infringed is certain text that appears on the following websites: www.rustbullet.com www.rustbullet.net , www.itkillsrust.com , www.itkillsrust.net, www.caswellplating.com , www.therusthut.net , www.stoprust.net , and www.eastcoastrustbullet.com . Further research may cause me to add to this list.

2) See attached word document. Some are sponsored links, most of the pages link to one or more of the offending sites.

3) You may reach me at jtlefave@yahoo.com .

4) See # 1 above, you may contact each owner/administrator directly through their websites, see the "contact us" function on their respective homepages.

5) "I have a good faith belief that the use of the copyrighted materials described above on the allegedly infringing web pages is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law."

6) "I affirm, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification is accurate and that I am the copyright owner or am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed."
